	</div> -->

	<div class="light">
		<div class="fixed left-0 top-0 -z-10 h-full w-full"><div class="relative h-full w-full bg-white"><div class="absolute bottom-0 left-0 right-0 top-0 bg-[linear-gradient(to_right,#4f4f4f2e_1px,transparent_1px),linear-gradient(to_bottom,#4f4f4f2e_1px,transparent_1px)] bg-[size:14px_24px] [mask-image:radial-gradient(ellipse_80%_50%_at_50%_0%,#000_70%,transparent_110%)]"></div></div></div>



		<div class="grid place-content-center w-full gap-2">
			<div class="relative mx-auto flex max-w-xl flex-col items-center">
				<h1 class="opacity-70 sm:pb-4 sm:mt-8 mt-4 text-center font-bold text-3xl text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-50 sm:text-5xl">
					<a href="/">¿Qué <span class="animate-text-gradient inline-flex bg-gradient-to-r from-neutral-900 via-slate-500 to-neutral-500 bg-[200%_auto] bg-clip-text leading-tight text-transparent dark:from-neutral-100 dark:via-slate-400 dark:to-neutral-400">comemos?</span></a>
				</h1>
				<p class="p-2 mt-6 text-center sm:text-lg leading-6 text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-200">
					Obtené la información nutricional de tus comidas en segundos. Subí una foto de tu plato y conocé qué estás comiendo.
				</p>
			</div>
			<section class="container max-w-xl h-64 flex flex-col items-center sm:mt-6 mt-3">
				<App client:idle />
			</section>
		</div>
	</div>
</Layout>

<style>

	h1 {
		font-family: Segoe UI Emoji, ui-sans-serif, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica Neue, Arial, Noto Sans, sans-serif, Apple Color Emoji, Segoe UI Emoji, Segoe UI Symbol, Noto Color Emoji;
	}

</style>
